Notes and suggestions:
- Bubble Sort will show far more comparisons and swaps for larger arrays; try increasing array size to 80–120 and watch the difference.
- Quick Sort here uses a simple middle pivot and is implemented non-recursively to allow incremental yields for animation; behavior can vary due to pivot choice.
- Merge Sort reports "assignments" (writes to the array) rather than swaps.
- You can tweak baseDelay in the script to slow/fast the visualization further.

